{"tid":1970303,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[正經食評]黃店代理 高質台灣拌麵推介","createTime":"2020-04-13T05:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T02:31:37.000Z","uid":132174,"like":24,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"53ac0532fa675669908c4ae5323c3f2e12fafd3a","tid":1970303,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先旨聲明</span></span>: 個代理係我親戚嘅朋友，呢包係佢送俾我嘅，但係我唔識得個代理本人，請自行定奪呢個post係咪廣告。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋呢隻麵係芫荽做嘅，討厭芫荽者請立即離開。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtaoUv4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtaoUv4.jpg&h=0809e8f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先價錢係$80四包，為起$20一包好似有啲貴，但係其實已經平過嗰啲X拌麵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講佢覺得佢個包裝似意大利粉多啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyPUgMg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyPUgMg.jpg&h=dcc3618c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢個麵條真係好彈！我未食過即食麵可以有咁嘅質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有其實佢個芫荽味唔係話太重。唯一我會挑剔嘅係唔夠辣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7Ew3xr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7Ew3xr.jpg&h=e3d61616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我會加埋之前杜汶澤yellopenrice介紹過嘅跑馬地消防焗麻辣醬，呢罐野係麻到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EvxZsZ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvxZsZ6.jpg&h=8b42533e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hF0sBTL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhF0sBTL.jpg&h=4f787902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃店Fced: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tyRiZ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tyRiZ0.jpg&h=2e36ab0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家隻麵聽講好似斷晒貨，起碼五月先有新貨，大家有興趣就記得密切留意佢IG: <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://instagram.com/mr.coriander.hk?igshid=vtsgsrs05bhm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmr.coriander.hk%3Figshid%3Dvtsgsrs05bhm&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=83ad5970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/mr.coriander.hk?igshid=vtsgsrs05bhm</a>"},{"pid":"e83392c9eb284d93e646cb3fd4c3bceab78be7ab","tid":1970303,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"最憎芫荽同埋太陽蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61abc9e523e0f0e6935fb1f699df1ed9cf9855f","tid":1970303,"uid":132174,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e83392c9eb284d93e646cb3fd4c3bceab78be7ab","tid":1970303,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"最憎芫荽同埋太陽蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"引戰狗請離開!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff225a69e7e3d032b08854feb2ce68c69326258","tid":1970303,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d61abc9e523e0f0e6935fb1f699df1ed9cf9855f","tid":1970303,"uid":132174,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e83392c9eb284d93e646cb3fd4c3bceab78be7ab","tid":1970303,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"最憎芫荽同埋太陽蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:15:44.000Z","